\end{aligned}
\]
Remove higher-order terms in \(\gamma_N\) and \(s\):
\[
\begin{aligned}
\mathbf{E}_{ij} &\approx \frac{g_{iN}g_{jN}}{s\chi_N} + s \frac{c_{iN} c_{jN}}{\chi_N}
\end{aligned}
\]
Sheehan arrives at (4.1):
